  ('locality-7fec267e-moex-00137', 'locality-7fec267e', 'locality-7fec267e-moex-112-b96fcbef', 'sub-locality-7fec267e-06', NULL, 'essay', '17 歲之甲將其壓歲錢新臺幣 10 萬元放入錢包，並持之向乙銀樓購買鑽
